      </div>
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-card-ico"><Icon name="zap" size={22} /></div>
        <strong>Stack with High-Carb Meals</strong>
        <p>ACV's blood sugar moderating effect is most pronounced with high-glycemic meals containing refined carbohydrates. If you eat bread, pasta, rice, or potatoes, taking ACV beforehand reduces the glucose spike and insulin response that promotes fat storage.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- TESTED BOX -->
